---
title: Mediterranean Quinoa Bowl with Kale Chips, Olives, and Feta
description: Quinoa bowls are a delicious way to enjoy this protein-rich seed - you can toss in any of your favourite mix-ins! This bowl packs major Mediterranean flavour with briny olives, tomatoes, salty feta, and fresh parsley. A crunchy topping of homemade kale chips adds a special twist to this easy weeknight recipe.
